Howard Lang https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Howard_Lang 0 Howard Lang (born Donald Yarranton, 20 March 1911 – 11 December 1989) was a British actor known for playing Captain William Baines in the BBC nautical drama The Onedin Line.
